summary: Here I am with another redraw!! Admiral-M-10K on Deviantart, for SOME reason, went through all my oldest crap. THEN they pointed...
caption:
Here I am with another redraw!! Admiral-M-10K on Deviantart, for SOME reason, went through all my oldest crap. THEN they pointed out that I should redraw this one. Me, being a sucker for redraw old things, naturally agreed that this needed to happen. The fun fact on this is the first one I drew back in the early days of digital art and I remember thinking that I’d never get used to drawing not on paper. That original took me 6 hours just to color. The redraw took me maybe 6 hours from start to finish. MAYBE. 


Commission info
Kofi
